WEBVTT

01:51.940 --> 01:52.419
Bro,

01:52.699 --> 01:53.979
I've packed up the merchandise.

01:54.179 --> 01:55.699
I'll call someone to pick it up.

01:56.660 --> 01:57.220
Okay.

02:08.220 --> 02:08.780
Wait a moment.

02:10.140 --> 02:10.860
What's up, bro?

02:11.419 --> 02:12.819
Do you need to add anything else?

02:13.979 --> 02:14.860
Send this over too.

02:15.780 --> 02:18.620
This... this is too big, isn't it?

02:18.620 --> 02:19.500
Can this be sent?

02:20.139 --> 02:21.419
And isn't this a promotional stand?

02:22.259 --> 02:23.340
This isn't merchandise either.

02:27.620 --> 02:28.180
You have a point.

02:42.139 --> 02:42.780
Now it's...

02:55.979 --> 02:58.859
Lawyer Xu, here's the thing.

03:03.819 --> 03:04.620
By the way,

03:04.859 --> 03:05.500
did you get any

03:05.500 --> 03:06.859
Shi Can's New Year's Eve merchandise?

03:08.259 --> 03:10.340
I had ten friends try to grab some,

03:10.340 --> 03:11.340
but none of us got any.

03:11.819 --> 03:13.460
If you have a special source,

03:13.579 --> 03:15.180
could you help me out?

03:15.340 --> 03:16.340
I'll ask around for you.

03:18.900 --> 03:20.220
That's disappointing.

03:22.460 --> 03:23.460
Li Shican

03:23.539 --> 03:24.620
just wanted to

03:25.060 --> 03:26.819
get it to her

03:26.819 --> 03:27.699
before New Year's.

03:28.180 --> 03:30.100
So he sent it here.

03:30.979 --> 03:32.060
I thought

03:32.340 --> 03:33.299
the guardian

03:33.299 --> 03:34.259
should know first,

03:34.539 --> 03:35.699
so I gave him the address.

03:40.900 --> 03:42.979
Was that kind or sneaky?

03:44.940 --> 03:46.139
What are you saying, Lawyer Xu?

03:48.180 --> 03:49.699
Nothing. Let's eat.

04:07.979 --> 04:09.660
Bro, I just saw the news online

04:09.739 --> 04:11.060
after the monthly exam.

04:11.060 --> 04:12.299
Is Sister Ruan Yu okay?

04:15.979 --> 04:17.940
Stop shaking it. Open it.

04:18.900 --> 04:20.220
I'll open it at home.

04:24.179 --> 04:24.700
Come on.

04:24.700 --> 04:26.340
This is my New Year's gift.

04:26.340 --> 04:27.460
Why are you in such a hurry?

04:29.979 --> 04:31.700
Can't I be curious?

04:38.299 --> 04:39.340
I see.

04:39.900 --> 04:40.539
You're so eager

04:40.539 --> 04:42.140
to let me open the New Year's gift.

04:42.379 --> 04:43.140
Is this gift

04:43.499 --> 04:44.900
prepared by you?

04:46.379 --> 04:47.100
Did you secretly

04:47.100 --> 04:48.379
collude with the Ministry of Culture and Entertainment

04:48.460 --> 04:49.820
to let me draw this gift?

04:49.820 --> 04:51.059
Are you

04:52.020 --> 04:53.260
going to play a prank to scare me?

04:54.580 --> 04:56.379
New Year's Eve is not April Fool's Day.

04:57.059 --> 04:58.260
I just think

04:58.499 --> 04:59.979
this box is quite exquisite.

05:00.780 --> 05:02.020
There must be something good inside.

05:03.020 --> 05:03.939
Really?

05:04.739 --> 05:06.220
Fine, let me see.

05:08.660 --> 05:09.460
Hold it for me.

05:13.539 --> 05:15.900
She's fine, but you might be in trouble.

05:16.580 --> 05:17.460
What does that mean?

05:28.780 --> 05:29.859
I hope this thing

05:30.059 --> 05:31.660
disappears from my sight immediately.

05:34.260 --> 05:35.220
Zhao Yi.

05:35.260 --> 05:36.299
Zhao Yi, I...

05:36.379 --> 05:37.179
This is the best New Year's gift

05:37.179 --> 05:39.780
I've ever received.

05:39.979 --> 05:42.580
That's great, I'm going to cry from being moved.

05:42.580 --> 05:44.179
Thank you, Sister Ruan Yu.

05:44.179 --> 05:45.939
I'm going to cry.

05:46.220 --> 05:47.260
That's great.

05:47.260 --> 05:48.179
What's the best?

05:48.179 --> 05:49.539
The New Year's gift is here.

05:49.539 --> 05:50.499
You haven't opened it yet.

05:50.979 --> 05:52.979
I'll only take one out of thousands.

05:53.340 --> 05:54.260
That's great.

05:56.260 --> 05:57.419
That's great.

08:03.700 --> 08:04.340
Ruan Yu,

08:05.020 --> 08:06.059
I'm heading back.

08:06.059 --> 08:06.979
Get some rest.

08:10.499 --> 08:11.539
Thank you, Lawyer Xu.

08:11.939 --> 08:12.460
It's okay.

08:12.739 --> 08:13.859
If you have any questions,

08:13.859 --> 08:15.020
just send me a message.

08:19.539 --> 08:20.580
Good night, Lawyer Xu.

08:20.700 --> 08:21.299
Good night.

08:47.420 --> 08:48.979
Baby, have a try.

08:50.060 --> 08:52.220
It's a new flavor. Delicious.

08:57.859 --> 08:58.499
What's wrong?

09:01.019 --> 09:02.300
I didn't draw Hanazawa Rui's

09:02.300 --> 09:03.220
New Year's gift again.

09:07.659 --> 09:09.979
It's okay. There are so many people.

09:09.979 --> 09:11.019
The probability is small.

09:11.300 --> 09:12.899
You still have a chance next time.

09:13.499 --> 09:14.659
No.

09:16.220 --> 09:17.220
This is the last New Year's Eve

09:17.340 --> 09:18.820
in high school.

09:24.180 --> 09:25.540
There's no chance anymore.

09:47.060 --> 09:47.619
Then

09:50.019 --> 09:52.259
I wish you a Happy New Year in advance.

09:53.859 --> 09:54.779
Is it reasonable enough?

10:17.739 --> 10:18.379
Mingying

10:19.460 --> 10:20.820
Why do I feel

10:21.779 --> 10:23.540
Xu Huaisong is

10:25.779 --> 10:26.580
flirting with me?

10:57.700 --> 10:59.580
-Where? -Let's meet for lunch.

11:03.379 --> 11:05.259
I'm at the office. There's an event today.

11:20.580 --> 11:21.779
I'll come to you as soon as I'm done.

11:22.139 --> 11:23.619
I didn't have dinner with you on our anniversary.

11:23.899 --> 11:24.979
Let's make up for it today.

11:28.540 --> 11:29.820
This restaurant is very good.

11:30.100 --> 11:31.619
It has your favorite Longjing Shrimp.

11:31.899 --> 11:32.859
Let's meet there later.

11:44.820 --> 11:46.739
I have something urgent to deal with, babe.

11:46.940 --> 11:48.300
I can't have dinner with you today.

11:50.619 --> 11:51.420
What's the matter?

11:51.779 --> 11:53.180
You don't even have time to eat dinner.

11:54.300 --> 11:55.259
A big deal.

13:51.180 --> 13:52.100
What are you looking at?

13:56.460 --> 13:57.859
I'm watching you play the piano.

13:58.139 --> 13:59.420
I didn't want to disturb you.

14:08.619 --> 14:09.779
Have some breakfast first.

14:27.979 --> 14:28.499
Ruan Yu,

14:28.700 --> 14:29.739
I have good news for you.

14:30.379 --> 14:31.540
Uncle Cen told me

14:31.700 --> 14:32.779
he has sent Cen Sisi

14:32.779 --> 14:33.540
abroad for treatment.

14:33.899 --> 14:35.100
She won't do anything

14:35.220 --> 14:36.060
to threaten your safety.

14:36.460 --> 14:37.820
You don't need to move again.

14:39.499 --> 14:40.220
That's great.

14:44.659 --> 14:45.420
Lawyer Xu,

14:46.700 --> 14:47.580
I can go home now.

14:50.300 --> 14:51.139
No rush.

14:51.340 --> 14:52.180
You can rest a few more days

14:52.180 --> 14:53.180
before going back.

14:54.420 --> 14:55.100
It's okay.

14:55.340 --> 14:56.659
I only have one suitcase.

14:56.700 --> 14:57.899
It won't take long to pack.

15:02.379 --> 15:02.940
If you want to move back

15:02.940 --> 15:04.019
today,

15:04.300 --> 15:05.180
I can pick you up.

15:07.499 --> 15:09.220
No, thanks for

15:09.220 --> 15:10.100
everything.

15:10.220 --> 15:11.379
If you're free later,

15:11.379 --> 15:12.379
let's have dinner.

15:13.220 --> 15:13.940
Lawyer Xu,

15:13.940 --> 15:15.019
I'll go pack up first.

15:17.220 --> 15:17.700
Bro,

15:18.659 --> 15:19.619
before the interview this afternoon,

15:19.619 --> 15:20.859
a director from a variety show team

15:20.859 --> 15:21.659
wants to meet you.

15:26.659 --> 15:27.700
But there's only

15:28.379 --> 15:29.420
there are only two hours.

15:30.300 --> 15:31.659
Brother Allen

15:32.139 --> 15:33.619
wants you to overcome the difficulties.

15:34.139 --> 15:34.700
I...

15:44.899 --> 15:46.580
No need. I really appreciate you

15:46.580 --> 15:47.619
for this.

15:47.619 --> 15:48.739
If you have time later,

15:48.739 --> 15:49.820
I'll invite you to dinner.

15:57.220 --> 15:59.700
OK, it's a deal.

16:49.180 --> 16:50.420
Put it there. I'll do it.

16:51.899 --> 16:52.820
Have breakfast first.

17:52.219 --> 17:53.139
Hello, Mr. He.

17:54.740 --> 17:55.300
It's me.

17:55.939 --> 17:57.100
Mr. He?

17:58.020 --> 17:59.100
Are you the one from No. 1 Middle School?

17:59.100 --> 17:59.859
Mr. He?

18:00.980 --> 18:02.500
You mean this Saturday?

18:15.379 --> 18:16.100
What's up, mom?

18:16.419 --> 18:17.100
Yu,

18:18.179 --> 18:19.340
your dad and I just got a call

18:19.340 --> 18:20.419
from Mrs. He.

18:20.820 --> 18:21.419
This Saturday

18:21.419 --> 18:22.379
is Mr. He's birthday.

18:22.580 --> 18:23.820
He invited us back to his hometown

18:24.139 --> 18:25.179
to attend his birthday party.

18:25.659 --> 18:27.260
Mrs. He invited you to go together?

18:27.820 --> 18:28.780
Do I have to go too?

18:29.020 --> 18:30.219
What? Do you have work to do?

18:31.500 --> 18:32.859
No, it's just...

18:33.699 --> 18:34.699
After Mr. He retired,

18:34.699 --> 18:35.459
he's been most concerned about

18:35.459 --> 18:36.699
his favorite students like you.

18:37.139 --> 18:38.020
Mrs. He is organizing it.

18:38.179 --> 18:38.980
If you should go, then go.

18:40.500 --> 18:42.139
Mom, have you had breakfast yet?

18:42.580 --> 18:43.300
Not yet.

18:43.300 --> 18:44.619
I'm drinking health tea with your dad.

18:45.419 --> 18:45.899
Did you hear

18:45.899 --> 18:46.939
what I said?

18:47.939 --> 18:48.899
I want to drink it too.

18:49.659 --> 18:50.179
Look,

18:50.740 --> 18:51.859
you're changing the subject.

18:51.859 --> 18:52.379
Are you

18:52.619 --> 18:53.500
selectively deaf?

18:55.219 --> 18:56.060
No, mom.

18:57.699 --> 18:59.100
I'll think about it.

18:59.179 --> 18:59.859
I'm hanging up now.

18:59.859 --> 19:00.859
Talk to you later, mom.

19:03.580 --> 19:04.740
Look at him, just hung up like that.

19:08.859 --> 19:09.459
Thank you.

19:09.659 --> 19:10.820
What would you like to drink?

19:14.300 --> 19:15.659
My mom made some health tea.

19:24.899 --> 19:27.419
I heard you mention your teacher earlier.

19:28.540 --> 19:29.859
You're still in touch

19:29.859 --> 19:30.899
with your teacher from back home?

19:30.899 --> 19:31.619
Not really,

19:32.100 --> 19:33.699
but I ran into her at a school event last time

19:33.899 --> 19:35.100
and exchanged numbers.

19:38.020 --> 19:39.060
Does she still remember you?

19:41.100 --> 19:42.100
She just called

19:42.300 --> 19:44.139
to invite me to her birthday party.

19:50.300 --> 19:51.219
Will you go?

19:57.820 --> 19:58.780
It depends.

19:58.939 --> 20:00.540
If I'm not busy with work.

20:01.859 --> 20:03.939
Right, you're so busy.

20:04.300 --> 20:05.459
If you're busy, just don't go.

20:19.300 --> 20:21.100
Lawyer Xu, I'm full.

20:22.260 --> 20:23.179
Just put it there.

20:23.179 --> 20:23.980
I'll clean up.

20:26.260 --> 20:26.859
Thank you.

20:30.500 --> 20:31.300
I'm leaving now.

20:35.179 --> 20:36.219
I'll walk you out.

20:36.699 --> 20:37.619
No, thanks, Lawyer Xu.

20:37.820 --> 20:38.939
I'll just call a taxi.

20:39.899 --> 20:40.619
Lawyer Xu,

20:41.980 --> 20:43.379
thank you for your

20:43.740 --> 20:44.699
consideration during this period.

20:45.859 --> 20:46.659
Thank you.

20:47.540 --> 20:48.260
You're welcome.

20:49.500 --> 20:50.260
I'll go now.

21:49.379 --> 21:50.500
I'll take you to experience

21:50.500 --> 21:51.659
the feeling of flying in a while.

22:10.780 --> 22:12.100
You're so pretty today.

22:16.699 --> 22:17.340
Baby,

22:18.060 --> 22:19.699
You look stunning today.

22:21.179 --> 22:21.699
Here's a rose

22:21.699 --> 22:22.980
for my favorite girl.

22:23.340 --> 22:24.139
Happy fifth anniversary.

22:26.100 --> 22:27.020
Happy fifth anniversary.

22:33.300 --> 22:34.340
Just because I liked you before,

22:34.340 --> 22:35.699
doesn't mean I like you now.

22:37.699 --> 22:40.219
If you don't like it, we'll change it.

22:41.500 --> 22:42.980
You've been meaning to say that, haven't you?

22:43.419 --> 22:45.100
What do you mean?

22:45.340 --> 22:45.980
Nothing.

22:53.699 --> 22:54.219
Please enjoy your meal.

22:54.379 --> 22:54.859
Thank you.

22:55.580 --> 22:56.740
Such a fancy restaurant,

22:56.740 --> 22:57.780
how could they get the order

22:57.780 --> 22:58.619
of the meal wrong?

22:58.980 --> 23:00.139
Why start with dessert?

23:00.219 --> 23:01.619
I asked them to serve the dessert first.

23:02.699 --> 23:03.219
Try it.

23:06.419 --> 23:07.699
You've prepared another surprise for me?

23:22.260 --> 23:23.139
Isn't this the engagement ring

23:23.139 --> 23:23.980
you gave me?

23:24.419 --> 23:24.980
Yes.

23:25.859 --> 23:27.699
What's the meaning of this, baby?

23:27.699 --> 23:29.219
I gave it to you,

23:29.419 --> 23:30.899
and now I'm giving it back.

23:31.699 --> 23:33.020
It's a full circle.

23:33.300 --> 23:34.419
Why are you giving it back?

23:35.899 --> 23:36.500
Baby,

23:37.340 --> 23:38.740
is there a misunderstanding?

23:39.219 --> 23:39.780
Is there?

23:41.179 --> 23:42.379
Five years of love,

23:42.500 --> 23:43.619
and now it's all

23:43.619 --> 23:45.260
deceit and betrayal.

23:46.219 --> 23:47.659
Is there any point in continuing?

23:49.580 --> 23:51.540
What deceit?

23:52.060 --> 23:53.419
I don't understand what you mean.

23:54.500 --> 23:55.020
Baby,

23:55.540 --> 23:56.740
did you misunderstand something?

23:58.619 --> 23:59.699
No matter what you misunderstand,

24:00.060 --> 24:00.780
I swear,

24:01.179 --> 24:02.699
since the day we were together,

24:02.699 --> 24:04.139
you are the only one in my heart.

24:04.580 --> 24:05.179
For so many years,

24:05.179 --> 24:06.260
I have always been like this.

24:06.260 --> 24:07.459
I'm the only one in your heart.

24:10.500 --> 24:11.260
What about her?

24:34.899 --> 24:35.780
Hello, room 602 for another night.

24:35.780 --> 24:36.699
Check out.

24:37.219 --> 24:38.139
Is it the room

24:38.139 --> 24:39.340
Mr. Zhang booked yesterday?

24:39.580 --> 24:40.179
Yes.

24:41.020 --> 24:43.060
Is it the same Mr. Zhang?

24:58.699 --> 24:59.740
It smells good.

25:00.500 --> 25:01.100
Try it.

25:02.580 --> 25:03.340
I won't share

25:03.340 --> 25:04.659
a dessert with someone else.

25:05.139 --> 25:05.939
The same goes for people.

25:06.619 --> 25:07.260
So you don't have to

25:07.260 --> 25:08.260
be hostile to me.

25:09.139 --> 25:09.780
I won't

25:09.780 --> 25:10.899
punish a woman

25:10.899 --> 25:11.699
who is also a victim

25:11.699 --> 25:12.899
for a man's mistake.

25:14.540 --> 25:15.540
Zhang Chuan doesn't deserve you.

25:16.100 --> 25:17.619
No unfaithful man

25:17.699 --> 25:18.459
deserves a woman

25:18.459 --> 25:19.260
who loves him.

25:24.899 --> 25:26.060
Then we...

25:30.859 --> 25:31.659
You want

25:32.780 --> 25:33.740
to punish him?

25:34.020 --> 25:34.899
That's exactly what I'm thinking.

25:40.459 --> 25:42.699
Zhang Chuan, you disgust me.

25:44.580 --> 25:45.980
Is this your big business?

25:46.260 --> 25:47.020
Director Zhang,

25:48.020 --> 25:49.659
today is your first day on the job.

25:49.780 --> 25:50.780
How do you feel?

25:52.859 --> 25:53.980
But I forgot to remind you,

25:54.780 --> 25:55.659
according to our

25:55.659 --> 25:56.580
employment contract,

25:56.980 --> 25:58.740
the company dismisses employees

25:59.100 --> 25:59.980
who violate moral standards.

26:03.939 --> 26:04.540
No.

26:05.179 --> 26:07.500
Mr. Gao, life is life,

26:07.500 --> 26:08.379
and work is work.

26:08.379 --> 26:09.859
They can't be mixed up.

26:09.899 --> 26:11.300
When you first approached me,

26:11.740 --> 26:12.580
wasn't it to change your work

26:12.580 --> 26:13.379
through

26:13.379 --> 26:14.580
your personal life?

26:15.540 --> 26:16.540
It's not like that, honey.

26:16.980 --> 26:17.899
Let me explain.

26:17.899 --> 26:18.580
Don't listen to her.

26:18.580 --> 26:19.459
It's not like that.

26:21.820 --> 26:22.540
No need to look.

26:23.020 --> 26:24.020
It's a dismissal notice.

26:32.379 --> 26:33.939
Did you plan this from the start,

26:34.619 --> 26:36.020
waiting to see

26:36.419 --> 26:37.500
how humiliating

26:37.500 --> 26:38.340
this moment would be for me?

26:38.459 --> 26:39.139
Exactly.

26:40.260 --> 26:41.780
Gao Qiuyan, don't forget,

26:41.780 --> 26:43.020
you're not exactly innocent yourself.

26:43.740 --> 26:46.060
You're the one who asked me to get in your car.

26:47.179 --> 26:48.179
See you next time, Mr. Gao.

26:51.179 --> 26:51.899
Together?

27:00.100 --> 27:00.899
Stay safe.

27:25.780 --> 27:26.780
I heard

27:27.060 --> 27:28.740
you've been having trouble closing deals

27:29.260 --> 27:30.260
with a few businesses in your live room.

27:43.260 --> 27:44.740
When you got in my car,

27:45.340 --> 27:46.740
you weren't wearing a ring.

27:46.740 --> 27:47.899
If it weren't for your last name,

27:47.899 --> 27:49.020
would I have gotten in your car?

27:49.580 --> 27:50.540
Was I wrong?

27:51.100 --> 27:52.060
I just wanted

27:52.060 --> 27:53.219
to give her a better life.

27:53.219 --> 27:54.419
Was I wrong?

27:56.459 --> 27:57.379
I went from

27:57.699 --> 27:59.340
a nobody with single-digit followers

27:59.340 --> 28:00.659
to having hundreds of thousands of fans,

28:00.659 --> 28:01.659
I know exactly

28:01.659 --> 28:02.540
how I got here,

28:02.540 --> 28:04.219
step by step.

28:04.699 --> 28:05.980
I've been broadcasting

28:06.980 --> 28:09.100
from midnight to 4 a.m.

28:09.100 --> 28:10.540
every day for three years

28:11.020 --> 28:12.500
without fail.

28:13.060 --> 28:14.740
Why shouldn't I get business deals?

28:15.260 --> 28:16.699
Why shouldn't I get more traffic?

28:16.820 --> 28:17.619
Are you done?

28:20.379 --> 28:21.899
Zhang Chuan, let me tell you.

28:22.540 --> 28:24.100
if hard work could guarantee success,

28:24.780 --> 28:26.219
the world would be

28:26.219 --> 28:27.300
overrun with successful people.

28:33.540 --> 28:34.340
Honey.

28:36.459 --> 28:37.060
Honey.

28:38.179 --> 28:38.780
Honey.

28:39.179 --> 28:40.379
Let me explain, honey.

28:40.699 --> 28:41.419
Honey.

28:42.459 --> 28:43.179
Honey.

28:43.899 --> 28:44.580
Honey.

28:47.619 --> 28:48.179
Can't you

28:48.179 --> 28:49.500
give me another chance?

28:50.179 --> 28:51.580
You bought me a car.

28:51.580 --> 28:53.060
I know you love me.

28:59.699 --> 29:01.260
Who said the car was for you?

29:02.260 --> 29:03.619
I got a text.

29:03.939 --> 29:04.740
Look.

29:08.379 --> 29:09.100
[Sorry.]

29:09.300 --> 29:11.459
[The number you dialed is invalid.]

29:12.219 --> 29:13.219
[Please check and redial.]

29:13.219 --> 29:14.260
You lied to me.

29:14.500 --> 29:15.060
Yeah.

29:16.699 --> 29:17.540
A virtual number

29:17.540 --> 29:19.139
can fool you around.

29:20.459 --> 29:21.219
Zhang Chuan,

29:22.379 --> 29:24.100
you shouldn't be so gullible.

29:26.300 --> 29:27.100
Shen Mingying,

29:27.300 --> 29:28.419
I've been with you for so many years,

29:28.419 --> 29:29.659
I've done my part.

29:29.899 --> 29:30.780
This car was the promise

29:30.780 --> 29:31.580
you made to me.

29:31.580 --> 29:33.060
What about your promise to me?

29:48.580 --> 29:51.740
Your 5th anniversary gift, take it back.

30:38.419 --> 30:39.179
Chuan.

30:40.500 --> 30:42.219
Chuan, what brings you here?

30:44.459 --> 30:46.179
I missed you.

30:46.260 --> 30:47.419
So you just come to see me?

30:47.820 --> 30:48.379
Come on.

30:50.780 --> 30:51.500
On the way,

30:51.500 --> 30:53.179
I saw a particularly beautiful bouquet of flowers.

30:53.419 --> 30:54.419
I thought of giving it to you.

30:56.939 --> 30:58.699
But it withered a bit on the way.

30:59.020 --> 31:00.540
I told you to take the train last time.

31:00.699 --> 31:02.260
You took the hard seat again, didn't you?

31:03.459 --> 31:04.340
After those dozen hours,

31:04.340 --> 31:05.300
can the flowers not wither?

31:09.859 --> 31:10.459
Baby,

31:11.139 --> 31:12.699
when I get transferred to work here,

31:13.139 --> 31:14.540
we can be together every day.

31:20.260 --> 31:20.980
What's wrong?

31:22.219 --> 31:23.740
The food we bought on the way is cold.

31:23.939 --> 31:24.899
We don't eat it.

31:34.619 --> 31:35.179
It's not cold.

31:36.340 --> 31:37.060
It's warm.

31:43.580 --> 31:44.780
I will work hard

31:45.219 --> 31:46.500
and buy you a big house in the future.

32:43.179 --> 32:43.859
It's one o'clock.

32:54.139 --> 32:55.659
Hello, Lawyer Xu.

32:58.260 --> 32:58.980
Have you eaten?

33:00.020 --> 33:00.899
I'm just about to go.

33:03.500 --> 33:04.899
Did you call me

33:05.219 --> 33:06.219
just to ask that?

33:08.699 --> 33:09.580
The judgment has come.

33:10.699 --> 33:11.540
If the other party

33:11.540 --> 33:12.899
doesn't appeal within 15 days,

33:13.100 --> 33:14.300
the judgment will take effect.

33:15.939 --> 33:17.100
Cen Sisi has already gone abroad.

33:17.100 --> 33:18.300
She shouldn't appeal, right?

33:19.820 --> 33:20.699
I just spoke with her father

33:20.699 --> 33:21.659
on the phone.

33:21.899 --> 33:22.699
Her father will announce

33:22.699 --> 33:23.980
the judgment result

33:24.219 --> 33:25.459
on her Weibo account,

33:25.820 --> 33:26.820
and also publish an

33:26.820 --> 33:27.740
apology statement.

33:28.100 --> 33:29.020
You can repost

33:29.020 --> 33:29.980
the Weibo post.

33:30.300 --> 33:32.219
Then the whole thing will be over.

33:32.699 --> 33:34.060
Okay, I'll do it now.

33:37.619 --> 33:38.340
Have your meal first.

33:39.780 --> 33:41.939
Have you eaten yet?

33:48.980 --> 33:49.659
I...

33:53.740 --> 33:54.300
haven't.

33:55.659 --> 33:56.740
Well, Lawyer Xu,

33:56.980 --> 33:58.500
you're only allowing the local official to set fire,

33:58.500 --> 33:59.659
but not allowing the common people to light lamps.

34:11.780 --> 34:12.619
I'll go right away.

34:13.699 --> 34:15.260
Okay, I'll hang up now.

34:21.900 --> 34:22.900
May I ask

34:23.619 --> 34:25.659
what made you, our esteemed Lawyer Xu,

34:26.299 --> 34:28.219
smile so cheaply?

34:39.819 --> 34:40.659
Have you eaten yet?

34:41.460 --> 34:42.420
I'm very busy with work.

34:43.060 --> 34:44.219
I haven't had time to eat yet.

34:45.779 --> 34:47.219
Has anyone cared about whether you've eaten or not?

34:47.779 --> 34:49.060
Before you asked me,

34:49.860 --> 34:50.940
no one cared about me.

34:53.339 --> 34:54.060
What are you doing?

34:55.420 --> 34:56.339
People who are cared about

34:56.339 --> 34:57.580
should go to eat.

34:58.619 --> 34:59.819
What about those who are not cared about?

35:00.540 --> 35:01.460
Do you want to join us?

35:04.699 --> 35:05.299
Let's go.

35:18.580 --> 35:19.900
Am I having an illusion?

35:21.259 --> 35:22.940
Dear netizens who are concerned about this,

35:23.060 --> 35:23.819
hello.

35:24.259 --> 35:25.779
I am Cen Sisi's father.

35:26.380 --> 35:27.500
Since Sisi is currently

35:27.500 --> 35:28.819
[undergoing treatment at the hospital,]

35:29.219 --> 35:31.259
[I'm posting this on her behalf.]

35:31.339 --> 35:32.500
[Regarding the infringement]

35:32.860 --> 35:34.259
[of the author Wen Xiang's reputation,]

35:34.259 --> 35:35.100
[we apologize.]

35:36.060 --> 35:38.139
[At the same time, we clarify]

35:38.580 --> 35:40.420
[that my daughter's extreme behavior]

35:40.619 --> 35:41.940
[was due to a mental illness]

35:42.299 --> 35:43.699
[and had nothing to do with the author Wen Xiang.]

35:44.259 --> 35:45.060
[Here,]

35:45.139 --> 35:46.900
[we extend our deepest apologies]

35:47.219 --> 35:48.819
[to Wen Xiang, the victim of this incident.]

35:49.380 --> 35:51.179
[We also hope that netizens]

35:51.179 --> 35:52.460
[stop making wild speculations]

35:52.739 --> 35:54.460
[and involving more innocent people.]

35:55.139 --> 35:57.540
[Thank you for your concern and understanding.]

36:06.420 --> 36:07.380
[True original works]

36:07.380 --> 36:08.540
[can withstand legal scrutiny.]

36:08.699 --> 36:10.299
[Wen Xiang, thank you for your hard work in protecting your rights.]

36:11.020 --> 36:12.420
[Finally, the dust has settled.]

36:12.619 --> 36:13.900
[Can "I Really Want to Whisper in Your Ear"]

36:13.900 --> 36:15.219
[resume its updates now?]

36:16.139 --> 36:17.259
[Wen Xiang, please start anew.]

36:17.500 --> 36:18.659
[We are all waiting for your return.]

36:27.420 --> 36:28.420
Then let's pick an auspicious day

36:28.580 --> 36:29.540
and start afresh.

36:38.179 --> 36:40.020
Looks like Ruan Yu's in a good mood.

36:41.020 --> 36:42.139
He just posted something

36:42.380 --> 36:42.739
about

36:42.739 --> 36:44.060
starting afresh.

36:44.980 --> 36:45.980
He's not dwelling on it at all.

36:45.980 --> 36:47.259
He said something about a birthday party.

36:53.020 --> 36:55.020
Rest up and start afresh.

36:56.980 --> 36:58.259
He's really a dad-type lawyer.

37:00.500 --> 37:01.259
Yu,

37:01.460 --> 37:02.339
don't forget

37:02.339 --> 37:03.460
Mr. He's birthday party.

37:09.179 --> 37:09.940
Tell me.

37:10.420 --> 37:11.739
What can I do for you?

37:14.060 --> 37:16.139
Brotherhood is what I want,

37:16.540 --> 37:18.860
so is my conscience.

37:19.339 --> 37:21.460
I can't have both.

37:25.940 --> 37:27.739
Retake that photo.

37:30.619 --> 37:31.420
Why?

37:33.259 --> 37:34.500
It's a good one.

37:35.100 --> 37:36.339
I look so smart

37:36.339 --> 37:37.380
from my hair

37:38.420 --> 37:39.380
to my toes.

37:39.460 --> 37:40.779
You're so narcissistic.

37:41.540 --> 37:42.219
How about this?

37:43.060 --> 37:44.860
Post another one on the moment.

37:45.219 --> 37:45.940
Post what?

37:46.540 --> 37:47.659
The case is over.

37:47.940 --> 37:49.060
I can't ruin my reputation.

37:49.779 --> 37:50.699
Xu Huaisong,

37:50.900 --> 37:52.380
will you go to the birthday party?

37:58.739 --> 38:00.179
We are both lawyers.

38:00.380 --> 38:01.819
Why are we so different?

38:07.460 --> 38:08.540
Tuesday morning.

38:09.060 --> 38:10.259
That's my lawsuit.

38:11.179 --> 38:13.259
The one on the right has a meeting on Saturday.

38:13.739 --> 38:15.060
Could it be

38:15.060 --> 38:16.619
Xu Huaisong's schedule?

38:20.179 --> 38:22.259
Only two work plans in a week.

38:23.060 --> 38:24.500
What kind of lawyer is this?

38:31.860 --> 38:33.460
Lawyer Xu, of course.

38:36.259 --> 38:37.259
In that case,

38:38.179 --> 38:38.980
he shouldn't have time

38:38.980 --> 38:40.020
to attend the birthday party, right?

38:44.259 --> 38:45.100
Okay, mom.

38:45.100 --> 38:46.739
I'll go with you.

38:56.219 --> 38:56.900
Eat more.

38:59.619 --> 39:00.460
What are you doing?

39:01.460 --> 39:04.060
I'm exhausted. I need to eat something.

39:04.699 --> 39:05.819
Don't look at me like that.

39:05.819 --> 39:06.819
This won't make you fat.

39:07.339 --> 39:08.739
I have some too.

39:10.060 --> 39:11.739
This QQ has zero fat.

39:12.020 --> 39:13.179
It's really suitable for you to eat.

39:14.699 --> 39:15.420
By the way,

39:15.819 --> 39:18.179
Mr. He's birthday party is on Saturday.

39:18.179 --> 39:19.060
Don't forget.

39:19.060 --> 39:20.380
Saturday, Mr. He.

39:21.060 --> 39:22.100
He didn't invite me.

39:23.179 --> 39:24.699
He probably still remembers the grudge

39:24.699 --> 39:25.339
I held against him

39:25.339 --> 39:26.659
in high school.

39:28.580 --> 39:29.779
Fine, I was actually thinking

39:29.779 --> 39:30.819
of going with you.

39:33.179 --> 39:34.460
Why aren't you at work today?

39:35.699 --> 39:37.779
I'm on vacation.

39:41.380 --> 39:42.060
Are you ready

39:42.060 --> 39:43.020
to start writing?

39:44.179 --> 39:45.460
You've been inspired

39:45.460 --> 39:46.659
by Xu Huaisong's place, right?

39:48.460 --> 39:49.299
To be honest,

39:50.219 --> 39:51.299
I've got some new ideas.

39:52.580 --> 39:53.219
Tell me.

39:55.299 --> 39:56.940
I want to add an urban extra chapter

39:56.940 --> 39:58.299
after the original ending.

39:59.420 --> 40:00.339
Many years later,

40:00.860 --> 40:01.500
the male and female leads

40:01.500 --> 40:03.179
reunite in a strange city.

40:04.060 --> 40:05.420
By chance,

40:06.100 --> 40:07.100
the female lead

40:07.580 --> 40:09.580
receives the New Year's gift

40:09.940 --> 40:11.460
from the male lead she's been longing for.

40:13.299 --> 40:14.980
Xu Huaisong gave you a New Year's gift?

40:16.940 --> 40:18.100
I've only been busy for two days,

40:18.659 --> 40:19.900
and you two have already

40:19.900 --> 40:21.580
skipped the old flame rekindling

40:21.699 --> 40:22.779
and fallen in love?

40:24.659 --> 40:25.460
No need to explain.

40:26.179 --> 40:26.779
When you're ready

40:26.779 --> 40:28.100
to give your originally tragic ending

40:28.100 --> 40:29.580
a new chapter,

40:30.299 --> 40:32.299
the answer is already clear.

40:34.460 --> 40:36.139
But what does Xu Huaisong

40:37.100 --> 40:38.540
giving you a New Year's gift mean?

40:38.900 --> 40:41.219
It definitely means something to you.

40:41.980 --> 40:44.259
What? You quit being an editor

40:44.580 --> 40:45.819
and become a love expert?

40:47.699 --> 40:48.580
Even if you are a love expert,

40:48.580 --> 40:50.619
you may not have a good relationship.

40:51.339 --> 40:51.980
But

40:52.980 --> 40:54.339
I, Shen Mingying's best friend,

40:54.739 --> 40:56.139
will never let her miss

40:56.139 --> 40:58.060
her happiness.

40:59.619 --> 41:01.819
His last name is Xu, not Fu.

41:03.860 --> 41:06.020
Fine, I'm a softy.

41:06.020 --> 41:07.100
You are always right.

41:07.100 --> 41:07.779
Fine.

41:08.420 --> 41:09.420
Alright, I'm done talking to you.

41:09.860 --> 41:10.980
I'm covered in sweat from my workout.

41:10.980 --> 41:11.699
I'm going to take a shower.

41:12.020 --> 41:12.540
Okay.

41:15.179 --> 41:16.179
You, the star athlete

41:16.179 --> 41:17.179
of our school's sports meet,

41:17.500 --> 41:18.779
I haven't seen you exercise

41:18.779 --> 41:19.900
since you started working.

41:20.420 --> 41:22.020
Today, the sun is rising in the west.

41:22.619 --> 41:24.659
No, the sun isn't rising in the west.

41:25.179 --> 41:26.619
It's just rising.

41:28.819 --> 41:29.420
I'm hanging up now.

41:30.179 --> 41:30.860
Go.

41:54.420 --> 41:55.739
Lawyer Liu, I saw

41:55.739 --> 41:57.179
the advertisement you posted on your WeChat Moment.

41:57.179 --> 41:58.940
I want to ask you something for my friend.

42:01.420 --> 42:02.500
What do you want to ask?

42:04.500 --> 42:06.540
It's my friend, not me.

42:08.020 --> 42:09.540
Then what does your friend want to ask?

42:10.819 --> 42:11.819
She was cheated on.

42:12.420 --> 42:13.179
Is there any way

42:13.179 --> 42:14.659
to punish her boyfriend?

42:15.739 --> 42:17.699
No, her ex-boyfriend.

42:19.619 --> 42:20.339
Punish?

42:20.819 --> 42:21.940
What do you mean by "punish"?

42:22.259 --> 42:23.659
What exactly are you looking for?

42:23.819 --> 42:24.659
If it's convenient,

42:24.659 --> 42:25.659
we should meet in person.

42:26.580 --> 42:28.299
It's not me,

42:28.299 --> 42:29.339
it's my friend.

42:32.259 --> 42:32.940
Then I suggest

42:32.940 --> 42:34.299
your friend should come

42:34.460 --> 42:35.699
if she has time.

42:38.299 --> 42:39.659
She might not have time,

42:39.940 --> 42:40.980
can I go in her place?

42:43.100 --> 42:43.980
If you know all the details

42:43.980 --> 42:44.900
the details between

42:44.900 --> 42:45.980
your friend and her ex,

42:46.100 --> 42:47.299
then that's fine.

42:48.619 --> 42:49.259
Okay.

43:01.860 --> 43:03.060
Miss Shen, sorry.

43:03.060 --> 43:04.100
Am I late?

43:04.580 --> 43:06.339
No, just in time.

43:07.100 --> 43:08.179
I didn't expect

43:08.179 --> 43:09.819
we'd meet again

43:10.020 --> 43:11.020
so soon.

43:11.219 --> 43:11.739
Yeah.

43:12.900 --> 43:14.500
I didn't really want to see you again.

43:15.460 --> 43:16.060
What are you talking about?

43:17.139 --> 43:17.699
Nothing.

43:18.259 --> 43:19.179
I don't know what you like to drink.

43:19.179 --> 43:20.380
I ordered an Americano. Is that okay?

43:21.020 --> 43:22.259
Sure, thank you.

43:22.500 --> 43:23.380
Excuse me, waiter.

43:23.380 --> 43:24.420
Can I have an orange juice, please?

43:24.420 --> 43:24.980
Okay.

43:28.179 --> 43:28.940
Orange C Americano.

43:31.219 --> 43:32.659
I'm sorry about last time.

43:32.900 --> 43:33.580
It was all a misunderstanding.

43:34.100 --> 43:35.580
I didn't expect a few words

43:35.580 --> 43:37.259
would hit a nerve.

43:37.259 --> 43:37.819
It's fine.

43:38.100 --> 43:38.940
I'm just

43:39.380 --> 43:40.900
perceptive in

43:40.900 --> 43:42.020
useless places.

43:42.299 --> 43:43.100
Right, well,

43:43.100 --> 43:44.339
I'm sorry I mistook you

43:44.500 --> 43:45.819
for a barmaid last time.

43:47.380 --> 43:48.619
Let's get down to business.

43:49.139 --> 43:51.179
Right, when did you...

43:52.339 --> 43:53.420
No, when did your friend

43:54.100 --> 43:54.819
find out

43:54.819 --> 43:55.900
her ex-boyfriend cheated?

43:56.819 --> 43:57.540
Yesterday.

43:58.500 --> 43:59.339
So, do you have

43:59.339 --> 44:00.460
any specific demands?

44:00.699 --> 44:01.619
Like,

44:01.619 --> 44:02.900
reimbursement for expenses during the relationship,

44:02.900 --> 44:04.219
or something extra...

44:04.219 --> 44:05.179
Not financial.

44:09.100 --> 44:10.460
Anything else?

47:14.619 --> 47:15.299
Hello, Dad?

47:16.619 --> 47:17.020
Okay.

47:17.179 --> 47:17.860
I'm heading out now.

49:08.339 --> 49:10.339
Huaishong.
